  "title": "🌟 Customer Experience Executive [No Experience Needed] 🌟",
  "description": "<h2>🎉 <strong>Build Meaningful Experiences. Grow Your Career.</strong></h2><p>Welcome to <strong>Valor Organisation</strong>, a dynamic marketing organisation based in Singapore. We focus on creating positive customer experiences through impactful campaigns and strong brand engagement. If you’re looking to develop practical skills in a fast-paced, people-oriented environment, this role is a great place to start.<br /></p><h3><strong>What You’ll Do</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Deliver positive and engaging customer experiences through marketing campaigns</p></li><li><p>Communicate with customers to represent brand values clearly and professionally</p></li><li><p>Support outreach initiatives while working closely with a driven team</p></li><li><p>Build strong communication, service, and interpersonal skills<br /></p></li></ul><h3><strong>What You’ll Gain</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Hands-on exposure to customer experience, marketing, and sales</p></li><li><p>A supportive team culture that values learning and collaboration</p></li><li><p>Opportunities for growth, development, and expanded exposure</p></li><li><p>Ongoing training and mentorship to support your career progression<br /></p></li></ul><h3><strong>Who We’re Looking For</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Fresh graduates, ORD-completed candidates, or career switchers</p></li><li><p>Individuals with a positive attitude and strong communication skills</p></li><li><p>Team players who are eager to learn and grow professionally<br /></p></li></ul><p>🚀 <strong>If you’re ready to build confidence, gain real-world experience, and grow in a customer-focused role, we’d love to hear from you.</strong></p>",
